<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="id"> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <title>Untuk My LOVEE ❤️</title> <style> body{ margin:0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff758c,#ff7eb3,#fad0c4); overflow:hidden; color:white; text-align:center; } #welcome{ position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4d6d,#ff758c,#ffb6c1); display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center; z-index:9999; animation:fadeOut 3s forwards; } #welcome h1{ font-size:3em; animation:zoomIn 1s ease; } #welcome p{ font-size:1.2em; animation:fadeIn 2s ease; } @keyframes zoomIn{ from{ transform:scale(0.5); opacity:0; } to{ transform:scale(1); opacity:1; } } @keyframes fadeIn{ from{opacity:0;} to{opacity:1;} } @keyframes fadeOut{ 0%,80%{opacity:1;} 100%{ opacity:0; visibility:hidden; } } .container{ padding:20px; position:relative; z-index:2; } h1{ font-size:2.5em; animation:beat 1s infinite; } @keyframes beat{ 0%,100%{transform:scale(1);} 50%{transform:scale(1.1);} } p{ font-size:1.1em; line-height:1.6; } button{ background:white; color:#ff4d6d; border:none; padding:12px 20px; border-radius:30px; font-size:1em; font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; } #special{ display:none; margin-top:20px; font-size:1.2em; font-weight:bold; color:#fff700; } #game{ position:relative; margin:20px auto; width:90%; max-width:400px; height:300px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden; } .heart{ position:absolute; font-size:2em; cursor:pointer; animation:fall linear forwards; } @keyframes fall{ from{top:-40px;} to{top:320px;} } #musicBtn{ position:fixed; bottom:20px; right:20px; background:white; color:#ff4d6d; border:none; padding:12px 18px; border-radius:30px; font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer; z-index:9999; } </style> </head> <body> <div id="welcome"> <h1>❤️ Selamat Datang ❤️</h1> <p>Ada sesuatu spesial untuk My LOVEE...</p> </div> <div class="container"> <h1>❤️ My LOVEE ❤️</h1> <p> Aku tahu kamu lagi capek dan banyak pikiran. Tapi aku mau kamu ingat kalau aku selalu bangga sama perjuanganmu. </p> <p> Terima kasih sudah bertahan sampai hari ini. Kamu hebat dan aku percaya kamu bisa melewati semuanya. </p> <p> <b>Semangat terus ya, My LOVEE 🌸</b> </p> <button onclick="showMessage()"> Klik kalau lagi capek 💌 </button> <div id="special"> Peluk virtual buat My LOVEE 🤗❤️ <br> Aku sayang kamu dan percaya kamu pasti bisa melewati hari ini 🌷 </div> <h2>🎮 Mini Game: Tangkap Hati! 🎮</h2> <div> Skor: <span id="score">0</span> </div> <div id="game"></div> </div> <audio id="musik" loop> <source src="lagu.mp3" type="audio/mpeg"> </audio> <button id="musicBtn" onclick="putarLagu()"> 🎵 Putar Lagu </button> <script> function showMessage(){ document.getElementById('special').style.display = 'block'; } let score = 0; const game = document.getElementById('game'); function createHeart(){ const heart = document.createElement('div'); heart.className = 'heart'; heart.innerHTML = '❤️'; heart.style.left = Math.random() * (game.clientWidth - 40) + 'px'; heart.style.animationDuration = (2 + Math.random() * 2) + 's'; heart.onclick = function(){ score++; document.getElementById('score').innerText = score; heart.remove(); if(score === 10){ alert( '🎉 Hebat! My LOVEE berhasil menangkap 10 hati! Aku makin bangga sama kamu ❤️' ); } }; game.appendChild(heart); setTimeout(() => heart.remove(), 4000); } setInterval(createHeart, 800); function putarLagu(){ document.getElementById('musik').play(); } </script> </body> </html>
